Install Java: Open terminal type "java" it gives some suggestions if java is not installed.
------------
> sudo apt-get install openjdk-8-jdk
> vi ~/.bashrc
Add the below line at the end.
export JAVA_HOME=/urs/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64
> echo $JAVA_HOME

Install Eclipse:
---------------
> sudo snap install --classic eclipse



  
